{"tid":2089708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登批港區國安法打擊自由 若當選將對中國祭新制裁","createTime":"2020-07-01T20:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T00:08:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c3909fe1c36708dda9bc7849fff5b490f9a58caa","tid":2089708,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T20:45:08.000Z","msg":"中央社華盛頓1日綜合外電報導）篤定代表美國民主黨角逐白宮大位的拜登今天表示，如果他當選美國總統，可能對中國實施新的經濟制裁。拜登還說中國實施「港區國安法」，對香港自由構成「致命打擊」。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n拜登表示，北京公布實施「港區國安法」的行徑未受懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n拜登提供給路透社的聲明提到：「北京的新國安法制定過程黑箱作業、規範範疇廣泛，對於讓香港不同於中國其他地區的自由、自治，已經構成致命的一擊。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登表示，如果自己當選美國總統，他將「禁止美國企業幫助壓迫和支持中國共產黨的國家監控」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登還說，如果北京「試圖讓美國公民、企業與機構噤聲，不讓他們行使（美國）憲法第一修正案保障的權利」，他將「迅速實施經濟制裁」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;（譯者：楊昭彥）1090702<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202007020007.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202007020007.aspx&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9TnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=a1a77a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202007020007.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"2efc5f9d1d5a3e31e173fea82ce31cb27b4d90a6","tid":2089708,"uid":154486,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T20:46:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦老人癡呆<br />\nyou know the thing"},{"pid":"34beaad2a9ce276e63f38f27883db8b364708e08","tid":2089708,"uid":41545,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T20:50:13.000Z","msg":"拜登你同你家族show晒斷共証據先信下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811a6436dde31ea50e9b64b4cab45d9e32a03083","tid":2089708,"uid":35763,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T20:51:39.000Z","msg":"老實講 我都唔鍾意拜登 但希望大家唔好all in侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"